+----------------+
|Game Description|
+----------------+

Help Anna solve the ancient riddle and find the amulet! Travel the world, dodge evil traps, and unravel fascinating secrets! But hurry - you have only three days to catch the criminals in this hidden object detective game!

+----------------------------------+
|Instructions / System Requirements|
+----------------------------------+

No install or crack is required for this portable version. Extract the ZIP file and create a shortcut to the executable (EXE) to play.

- Windows Vista, Windows XP, Windows 7

- Pentium-III processor speed

- 256 MB RAM

- 64 MB VRAM 16 or 32-bit Video Card

- 16 bit DirectX compatible sound card

- DirectX 1.0

